1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:34,780 --> 00:01:40,570
[Bazaar Beloved Birds]

3
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:43,650
[Episode 16]

4
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:47,750
You know the state you're in when you go mad,

5
00:01:47,970 --> 00:01:49,009
losing all reason,

6
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,210
posing a danger

7
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,590
to those near.

8
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:57,150
I know what you're thinking.

9
00:01:57,450 --> 00:01:59,070
Even if you transform into Demon Boy,

10
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,830
you won't escape.

11
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:03,110
In my Lu Ming Manor,

12
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,940
incense that can clear your mind

13
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:07,550
burns everywhere.

14
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:10,300
In here,

15
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,530
you can't transform.

16
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:15,710
What exactly do you want to know?

17
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:19,560
Thirteen years ago,

18
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,820
who rescued you?

19
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,430
I've said it many times.

20
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:27,950
I really don't know.

21
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:30,480
All the memories before I became Yu Zhao

22
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:31,780
are blurred.

23
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,090
I only remember a widespread fire.

24
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:39,560
And someone was calling my name.

25
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:41,310
Zihe!

26
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,030
Zihe!

27
00:02:44,829 --> 00:02:45,550
Zihe!

28
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,110
Zihe!

29
00:02:53,810 --> 00:02:56,890
It seems your memory hasn't fully recovered.

30
00:02:57,250 --> 00:02:58,290
In that case,

31
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:02,080
as the Sword Master, I've got to help you, Young Master Feng.

32
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:06,420
What do you want to do to Young Master Feng?

33
00:03:09,350 --> 00:03:12,190
He has a nickname, the Eight-Armed Holy Doctor.

34
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,270
There's no illness he can't cure.

35
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,590
I believe

36
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:16,790
he

37
00:03:17,190 --> 00:03:19,190
can help you remember.

38
00:03:31,370 --> 00:03:32,370
What should we do?

39
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,590
How do we face Chief Feng

40
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:35,240
in the underworld?

41
00:03:35,350 --> 00:03:36,590
Stop nagging.

42
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:39,220
We can't do anything now.

43
00:03:39,970 --> 00:03:41,970
We can only watch and wait.

44
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,240
Master, you've already obtained the Demon Boy.

45
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,520
You're already the Chief of Sects.

46
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:08,640
Does it really matter

47
00:04:09,010 --> 00:04:09,700
who saved Feng Zihe?

48
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,510
Of course.

49
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:14,710
This concerns the whereabouts of the Laugh Master's Red Jade.

50
00:04:15,130 --> 00:04:16,610
I can only complete the set of the three Red Jades

51
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:19,510
of Master Knife, Sword and Laugh

52
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:20,390
once I obtain that Red Jade.

53
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:22,490
The Demon Boy is just a distraction.

54
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:25,570
The real importance lies in the secret behind him.

55
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:27,930
Behind the three masters' Red Jades

56
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,270
hides a treasure.

57
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:30,270
It is said that

58
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,950
whoever obtains this treasure

59
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:34,570
will become the true supreme in the martial world.

60
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:37,430
As for the position of the Chief of Sects, which holds no real authority,

61
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,580
it's just an added perk.

62
00:04:40,650 --> 00:04:41,550
Also,

63
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:43,080
a distraction tactic.

64
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:44,630
Your thoughts are meticulous.

65
00:04:44,909 --> 00:04:45,710
I admire you.

66
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,470
Let's go.

67
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,950
Today, I gathered everyone here

68
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,790
because there's something I need to share with you.

69
00:04:56,990 --> 00:04:58,280
We're going to rescue Yu Zhao together.

70
00:05:00,250 --> 00:05:01,450
Yesterday, Miss Liu and I discussed the matters

71
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,130
concerning Lu Ming Manor and Ye Yunqing.

72
00:05:03,790 --> 00:05:04,910
I feel like we can't wait any longer.

73
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,210
So I need your help.

74
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:09,420
Miss, tell us.

75
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,800
What do you suggest we do?

76
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:12,550
Firstly, we need to accomplish three things:

77
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:14,390
money, manpower, and the location.

78
00:05:14,970 --> 00:05:15,630
Starting with money.

79
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:16,830
Saving him from Lu Ming Manor

80
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,780
is not an easy task.

81
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,120
We need to devise

82
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,110
an exceptionally perfect plan,

83
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:21,670
which requires a lot of money.

84
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:22,950
Uncle San,

85
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:26,030
how much money is currently in the Huixian Restaurant's account?

86
00:05:27,230 --> 00:05:27,710
Miss,

87
00:05:28,710 --> 00:05:29,510
there's no money.

88
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:36,470
The funds from the Yu family

89
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,680
and Huixian Restaurant

90
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:40,880
were taken by Lu Ming Manor's people.

91
00:05:40,909 --> 00:05:42,430
But Huixian Restaurant is still in operation.

92
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:44,220
Can't it generate income?

93
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,080
Miss, you have no idea.

94
00:05:47,110 --> 00:05:48,080
Since Young Master left,

95
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,520
for some unknown reason,

96
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:52,050
the business of Huixian Restaurant has plummeted.

97
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,400
If it continues like this,

98
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,340
it won't be long

99
00:05:55,930 --> 00:05:57,930
before it has to close.

100
00:05:58,230 --> 00:05:58,710
No.

101
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,310
No, Yu Zhao hasn't come back yet.

102
00:06:00,550 --> 00:06:01,430
Huixian Restaurant can't be closed.

103
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:02,590
Xiang,

104
00:06:03,110 --> 00:06:04,630
go and pawn everything valuable from the Yu Mansion.

105
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:05,780
Also, the things in my room.

106
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:06,870
Miss,

107
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:09,470
those are your most precious belongings.

108
00:06:09,990 --> 00:06:11,150
Are you sure?

109
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:14,990
Pawn them all.

110
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,270
Some useful things,

111
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,190
I've already taken them out.

112
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:18,900
As for the rest,

113
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,360
pawn as much as you can.

114
00:06:22,150 --> 00:06:22,750
Okay.

115
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:23,470
Also, Xiang,

116
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,750
the money obtained from the pawning,

117
00:06:24,770 --> 00:06:26,210
allocate a portion as subsidy for Huixian Restaurant,

118
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,110
and the remaining amount

119
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,520
will be used to rescue Yu Zhao.

120
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:29,770
Yes, Miss.

121
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:31,190
Uncle San,

122
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,370
I'll entrust Huixian Restaurant in your hands.

123
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,990
Miss, rest assured.

124
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:36,270
With Uncle San in charge,

125
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:37,580
Huixian Restaurant is in good hands.

126
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:40,659
Next

127
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:41,750
is manpower.

128
00:06:42,890 --> 00:06:44,170
We need some experts

129
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,950
who can sneak into Lu Ming Manor to rescue Yu Zhao.

130
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:47,950
Jin Gang,

131
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:49,310
I know you have some reservations about me.

132
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:50,070
That's fine.

133
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:51,310
I don't need you to change your mind.

134
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,190
But this time, I need your help.

135
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:56,150
You are familiar with various factions in Xianyun City.

136
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:57,990
I need you to help me find a group of experts.

137
00:06:58,350 --> 00:06:59,150
No matter the cost,

138
00:06:59,550 --> 00:07:00,590
as long as they are skilled.

139
00:07:00,810 --> 00:07:02,270
I trust you in this matter.

140
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:03,470
Okay. No problem.

141
00:07:04,670 --> 00:07:05,270
Mengniang,

142
00:07:05,530 --> 00:07:07,100
you go and help Jin Gang.

143
00:07:09,030 --> 00:07:09,950
Okay, sister.

144
00:07:18,230 --> 00:07:20,240
Next is the location.

145
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:22,070
We need to know where Lu Ming Manor is.

146
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:25,990
Exactly.

147
00:07:26,570 --> 00:07:28,770
Where is Lu Ming Manor?

148
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:33,180
I do have a rough idea of its location.

149
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:34,870
Tell us. Where is it?

150
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,870
I've heard my father mention it.

151
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:39,060
It is located in a bamboo forest

152
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,340
about 30 miles west of Xianyun City.

153
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,230
But...

154
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:43,400
What?

155
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:45,870
For safety, Lu Ming Manor

156
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,800
has turned the bamboo forest into a maze.

157
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:49,470
Without a guide,

158
00:07:49,590 --> 00:07:50,950
ordinary people can't find the entrance at all.

159
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:52,830
Moreover, deep in the bamboo forest,

160
00:07:52,970 --> 00:07:54,210
there are many traps.

161
00:07:54,350 --> 00:07:56,470
A little carelessness not only leads to being unable to find the entrance

162
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,710
but also getting trapped inside.

163
00:07:59,030 --> 00:07:59,390
Well...

164
00:07:59,400 --> 00:07:59,850
Well...

165
00:08:01,150 --> 00:08:02,350
Did your father tell you

166
00:08:02,370 --> 00:08:03,280
where the entrance is?

167
00:08:04,710 --> 00:08:05,920
My father doesn't know either.

168
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:08,270
Every time he went to Lu Ming Manor,

169
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,070
he waited outside the bamboo forest.

170
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,830
Master Ye would send people to guide him in.

171
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,120
Never mind.

172
00:08:15,290 --> 00:08:16,890
Let's stick to the plan,

173
00:08:16,970 --> 00:08:17,780
make money, recruit manpower,

174
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:19,950
and then separately investigate the location of Lu Ming Manor,

175
00:08:20,470 --> 00:08:21,750
especially in places

176
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:22,750
where those martial artists frequent the most.

177
00:08:24,690 --> 00:08:25,240
Okay.

178
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,520
Starting from today,

179
00:08:27,810 --> 00:08:28,780
to show our determination,

180
00:08:29,310 --> 00:08:30,300
Huixian Restaurant will be renamed.

181
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,320
Xiang.

182
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:41,370
[Zhao Xi Restaurant]

183
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:39,080
Huixian Restaurant will be renamed as Zhao Xi Restaurant.

184
00:08:41,990 --> 00:08:42,510
Jin Gang,

185
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,830
find someone to hang up the new sign.

186
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:44,790
Yes, Miss.

187
00:08:49,110 --> 00:08:50,910
Alright, everyone, go about your tasks.

188
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:51,350
Okay.

189
00:08:55,570 --> 00:08:56,130
Let's go.

190
00:09:07,890 --> 00:09:11,700
[Divorce Agreement]

191
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,240
Yu Zhao, wait for me.

192
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,620
This time, it's my turn to rescue you.

193
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:57,800
Go on.

194
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:01,820
Is there anything else

195
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,640
that has come to your mind?

196
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:09,860
How is it?

197
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,520
Back then,

198
00:10:10,710 --> 00:10:13,230
a skilled master sealed off Young Master Feng's seven meridians and eight pulses,

199
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:15,250
thereby blocking his memories.

200
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:17,950
I have been trying to open up his meridians,

201
00:10:18,050 --> 00:10:19,090
but without success.

202
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,430
Please don't be angry, Master.

203
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:24,210
Although the meridians haven't been opened,

204
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:26,240
there has been some progress.

205
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:26,990
Tell me.

206
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:30,090
While stimulating his Baihui, Houding,

207
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:32,380
Fengfu, and Yamen acupoints,

208
00:10:32,410 --> 00:10:33,720
I noticed a brief restoration

209
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,480
of Young Master Feng's memory.

210
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:37,680
However, it's all very vague.

211
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:39,210
What did he say?

212
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:42,820
Hai.

213
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,140
Hai?

214
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,150
Hai Liyuan?

215
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:52,660
It's really him.

216
00:10:52,990 --> 00:10:54,310
It looks like I was right.

217
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:55,830
Thirteen years ago,

218
00:10:55,850 --> 00:10:58,170
Hai Liyuan rescued Feng Zihe

219
00:10:58,350 --> 00:11:00,400
and took the Red Jade of Cangqiong.

220
00:11:01,110 --> 00:11:02,190
To keep the secret,

221
00:11:02,310 --> 00:11:04,390
he and his wife took poison together and died.

222
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:06,480
Now, it all makes sense.

223
00:11:07,630 --> 00:11:09,670
Hai Liyuan arranged for Bai Linglong

224
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:11,530
to bring Feng Zihe to Xianyun City.

225
00:11:12,190 --> 00:11:13,870
Bai Linglong changed her name to Zang Muxiang.

226
00:11:14,430 --> 00:11:16,320
To protect Feng Zihe's identity,

227
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,840
she sealed his memories

228
00:11:20,540 --> 00:11:21,980
and renamed him Yu Zhao,

229
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:24,590
claiming him as her own biological son.

230
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:26,590
Then,

231
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:28,050
who is this Yu Xixi?

232
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,560
Xixi.

233
00:11:33,070 --> 00:11:34,070
Keep asking.

234
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,510
See if you can find out

235
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:38,560
where Hai Liyuan's Red Jade of Cangqiong is.

236
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:39,950
Yes.

237
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,550
Keep a close eye on the Yu Mansion.

238
00:11:54,830 --> 00:11:56,710
The Red Jade of Cangqiong belonging to the Laugh Master

239
00:11:56,870 --> 00:11:58,470
must be related to the Yu Mansion.

240
00:11:58,950 --> 00:11:59,390
Yes.

241
00:12:00,010 --> 00:12:00,570
Also,

242
00:12:01,170 --> 00:12:01,970
release the news

243
00:12:02,850 --> 00:12:03,530
that the Feng Slaughtering Conference

244
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:05,750
will be held in 3 days in the bamboo forest

245
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:07,970
outside the manor.

246
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,050
By then,

247
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:12,310
Feng Zihe will be publicly executed.

248
00:12:12,950 --> 00:12:14,040
Execute Feng Zihe?

249
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:14,910
But

250
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:16,740
weren't you planning to keep Feng Zihe alive

251
00:12:17,210 --> 00:12:18,250
to command the martial world?

252
00:12:19,590 --> 00:12:22,240
This is the only way to attract those who will come to his rescue.

253
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:24,580
The hidden secrets behind this

254
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:26,850
will soon come to light.

255
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:29,350
Interesting.

256
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:32,070
It's getting more and more interesting.

257
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,070
Young Master Feng,

258
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:49,360
you haven't eaten anything for days.

259
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:50,830
Please eat something.

260
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,940
If you have any requests,

261
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,060
just let me know.

262
00:12:55,140 --> 00:12:56,370
I still can't understand

263
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:58,060
how the you from childhood,

264
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:00,880
so refined and elegant,

265
00:13:01,430 --> 00:13:02,470
has become

266
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,030
the Demon Boy of the martial world,

267
00:13:04,290 --> 00:13:05,820
ending up in such a situation.

268
00:13:08,470 --> 00:13:09,600
Did you know me before?

269
00:13:17,620 --> 00:13:18,740
To be honest,

270
00:13:19,260 --> 00:13:20,420
when I was young,

271
00:13:20,630 --> 00:13:22,530
I worked as a cook in the Golden Blade Sect.

272
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,390
Then, how did you end up here?

273
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:28,370
In the current state of the world,

274
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:30,990
life is getting tougher.

275
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:32,630
To support my family,

276
00:13:32,910 --> 00:13:35,630
I came to Lu Ming Manor to work.

277
00:13:36,990 --> 00:13:38,490
Just now, you mentioned my childhood?

278
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:39,630
Yes.

279
00:13:40,030 --> 00:13:41,350
Since you were a kid,

280
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:44,350
you've always been refined and exceptionally talented.

281
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:48,030
And you treated us servants well.

282
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,590
Everyone in the Golden Blade Sect

283
00:13:49,770 --> 00:13:52,370
admired you greatly.

284
00:13:53,230 --> 00:13:54,270
What a pity.

285
00:13:55,430 --> 00:13:56,880
Times have changed.

